    "body": "Yeah...this is a tough one.  When I initially worked on this, I really didn't want to coerce to `float` given how lossy that could be in cases like this.  That being said, if you're passing in `coerce`, does that mean you're willing to accept lossiness in return for coercing every entry to some kind of number?\r\n\r\n@fakio : What would you personally prefer?\r\n\r\ncc @jreback "
